verbose_text: There was no effect observed from the growth curve after exogenous gene hspA was cloned into L. lactis NZ3900; different concentrations of Nisin did not affect the growth of NZ3900 and NZ3900 / pNZ8110, while different concentrations of Nisin inhibited the growth of NZ3900 / pNZ8110-hspA except 10 ng/mL Nisin.
evidence: Nisin inhibited the growth of NZ3900/pNZ8110-hspA except 10 ng/mL Nisin
